	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pauca scribo, quoniam iamiam abiturus est hic noster.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2" cert="high">Arovię</placeName> actum, ex vestris legatis cognovisti.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Hie hätt üwer schreiben und das zemmenkommen zuͦ <placeName ref="l2" cert="high">Arow</placeName> sovil bracht, das der handel wider wirt für räth und burger kommen.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die botten sind wol verritten gen <placeName ref="l21" cert="high">Baden</placeName>; man wirt inen aber nachschryben.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Uff hütt sind all min herren, die uß sind, beschriben.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid interim sperem, nescio.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die gmein burgerschafft wär guͦt; <foreign xml:lang="la">capita sunt aegra.</foreign></s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Putant multi,</foreign> man mögs wol böser, aber nitt beßer machen.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nos nostrum praestamus officium; singulis concionibus declamamus de hac de omnes, accedimus etiam senatum, ut proxime scripsi.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed eo redeunt nostri evangelici, ut parum curent illud OS DOMINI LOQUUTUM EST.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expecto, quid tu per <persName ref="p4191" cert="high">Apiarium</persName> scribas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quas hic mitto, heri a <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvino</persName> accepi.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Petri Martyris</persName> literas, apertae cum essent, legi.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de">Mitt <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genff</placeName> hoff ich wird sich die sach zuuͦ guͦtem zien;</foreign> non ausim scribere, qualiter cum illis agatur; sed ipsi pro sua prudentia pulchre sustinent importunitatem, ne dicant improbitatem hanc.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Forte de his <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvinus</persName> aliqua; is quasi in signum positus est, cui contradicitur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Raptim.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Fratri salutem dicas; non potui illi nunc scribere.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvi sint tui omnes.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName>, 28. octobris 1555.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[oannes] H[allerus</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3544" cert="high">Wolphgango ab Erlach</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l21" cert="high">Badenam</placeName> proficiscenti omnes scripturae locos exscripsi, et omnia alia argumenta quum ex tuis literis tum aliunde ad hanc rem pertinentia collecta tradidi cum quibusdam etiam locis ex Patribus et iure canonico <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculi</persName> opera conquisitis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf...:]</note>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinę</placeName> ecclesię pastori fidelissimo, domino et compatri suo charissimo.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="de" type="auto">M. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrych Bullingern</persName> zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName></s>
				</p>
			</div>
